{
  "texts": [
    "Existing vehicle motion generation methods cannot directly generate motion purely from text and the scene map.",
    "To solve the problem, here we propose a novel text-to-motion method.",
    "The key idea is linking a placement and planning module as role functions with LLMs to extract and turn motion attributes into coordinates.",
    "Motion attributes include position attributes (e.g., distance, direction) and movement attributes (e.g., speed, action).",
    "For the placement module, we endow each lane node in the lane map with its attributes to match with the position attributes."
  ]
}